        <content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:1111/blog/arch-install-notes/">&lt;p&gt;These are my personal install notes, kept here so I can reproduce my setup
without digging through the wiki every time.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;assumptions&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#assumptions&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: assumptions&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;Assumptions&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UEFI system&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NVMe drive at &lt;code&gt;&#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Btrfs with subvolumes for easy snapshotting&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;partition-layout&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#partition-layout&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: partition-layout&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;Partition layout&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #F8F8F2; background-color: #282A36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;plain&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;nvme0n1p1   512M    EFI System Partition&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;nvme0n1p2   rest    Linux filesystem (btrfs)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #F8F8F2; background-color: #282A36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;# partition the disk&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;fdisk&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;# format&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;mkfs.fat&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -F32&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1p1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;mkfs.btrfs&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -L&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; arch &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1p2&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;btrfs-subvolumes&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#btrfs-subvolumes&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: btrfs-subvolumes&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;Btrfs subvolumes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #F8F8F2; background-color: #282A36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;mount&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1p2 &#x2F;mnt&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;btrfs&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; subvolume create &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;@&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;btrfs&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; subvolume create &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;@home&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;btrfs&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; subvolume create &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;@snapshots&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;btrfs&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; subvolume create &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;@log&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;umount&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;mnt&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;# mount with options&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;mount&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -o&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; noatime,compress=zstd,subvol=@ &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1p2 &#x2F;mnt&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;mkdir&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -p&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;{home,.snapshots,var&#x2F;log,boot}&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;mount&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -o&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; noatime,compress=zstd,subvol=@home &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1p2 &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;home&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;mount&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -o&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; noatime,compress=zstd,subvol=@log &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1p2 &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;var&#x2F;log&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;mount&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nvme0n1p1 &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;boot&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;base-install&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#base-install&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: base-install&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;Base install&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #F8F8F2; background-color: #282A36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;pacstrap&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -K&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;mnt base base-devel linux linux-firmware&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; \&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;    btrfs-progs networkmanager neovim git zsh&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;bootloader-systemd-boot&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#bootloader-systemd-boot&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: bootloader-systemd-boot&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;Bootloader (systemd-boot)&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #F8F8F2; background-color: #282A36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;arch-chroot&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;mnt&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;bootctl&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; install&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;# &#x2F;boot&#x2F;loader&#x2F;loader.conf&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;cat&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; &amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;boot&#x2F;loader&#x2F;loader.conf&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; &amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &amp;#39;EOF&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;default arch.conf&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;timeout 3&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;console-mode max&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;editor no&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;EOF&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;# &#x2F;boot&#x2F;loader&#x2F;entries&#x2F;arch.conf&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;cat&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; &amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;boot&#x2F;loader&#x2F;entries&#x2F;arch.conf&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; &amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &amp;#39;EOF&amp;#39;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;title   Arch Linux&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;linux   &#x2F;vmlinuz-linux&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;initrd  &#x2F;initramfs-linux.img&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;options root=LABEL=arch rootflags=subvol=@ rw quiet&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;EOF&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;gotchas&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#gotchas&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: gotchas&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;Gotchas&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If snapper is used, the &lt;code&gt;.snapshots&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; directory must exist on the root
subvolume before mounting — otherwise snapper creates it as a regular dir
and the subvolume mount fails.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;compress=zstd&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; without a level defaults to level 3. Use &lt;code&gt;compress=zstd:1&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;
for speed or &lt;code&gt;zstd:9&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; for cold storage.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Don&#x27;t forget &lt;code&gt;btrfs-progs&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; in the initramfs hooks if you want fsck at boot.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That covers the basics. Next post will cover dotfiles and sway configuration.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
